trans-unit.source: Defines the contract for the collection used by ASP.NET session state to manage session.
trans-unit.target: ASP.NET 세션 상태에서 세션을 관리 하는 데 사용 하는 컬렉션에 대 한 계약을 정의 합니다.

trans-unit.source: The ISessionStateItemCollection interface defines the collection of session items exposed to application code by the <xref:System.Web.SessionState.HttpSessionStateContainer> class.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Web.SessionState.HttpSessionStateContainer>클래스</xref:System.Web.SessionState.HttpSessionStateContainer> 에서 응용 프로그램 코드에 노출 하는 세션 항목의 컬렉션을 정의 하는 ISessionStateItemCollection 인터페이스

trans-unit.source: The ASP.NET implementation of the ISessionStateItemCollection interface is the <xref:System.Web.SessionState.SessionStateItemCollection> class.
trans-unit.target: ISessionStateItemCollection 인터페이스의 ASP.NET 구현에는 <xref:System.Web.SessionState.SessionStateItemCollection>클래스</xref:System.Web.SessionState.SessionStateItemCollection> 입니다.

trans-unit.source: If you create a class derived from the <xref:System.Web.SessionState.SessionStateStoreProviderBase> class to store session data, you can either use the <xref:System.Web.SessionState.SessionStateItemCollection> class to manage the stored objects or implement the ISessionStateItemCollection interface on your own collection manager.
trans-unit.target: 파생 된 클래스를 만드는 경우는 <xref:System.Web.SessionState.SessionStateStoreProviderBase>세션 데이터를 저장할 클래스를 사용 하거나는 <xref:System.Web.SessionState.SessionStateItemCollection>저장된 된 개체를 관리 하거나 사용자 고유의 컬렉션 관리자에 ISessionStateItemCollection 인터페이스를 구현 하는 클래스입니다.</xref:System.Web.SessionState.SessionStateItemCollection> </xref:System.Web.SessionState.SessionStateStoreProviderBase>

trans-unit.source: If you implement the ISessionStateItemCollection interface, you must also create a class that inherits the <xref:System.Web.SessionState.SessionStateStoreProviderBase> class in order to make use of your ISessionStateItemCollection implementation to manage session variables.
trans-unit.target: 상속 하는 클래스도 만들어야 ISessionStateItemCollection 인터페이스를 구현 하는 경우는 <xref:System.Web.SessionState.SessionStateStoreProviderBase>확인 하기 위해 클래스 ISessionStateItemCollection 구현 세션 변수를 관리를 사용 하 여.</xref:System.Web.SessionState.SessionStateStoreProviderBase>

trans-unit.source: An ISessionStateItemCollection implementation must also implement the members of the <xref:System.Collections.ICollection> interface.
trans-unit.target: ISessionStateItemCollection 구현을의 멤버를 구현도 <xref:System.Collections.ICollection>인터페이스.</xref:System.Collections.ICollection>

trans-unit.source: Removes all values and keys from the session-state collection.
trans-unit.target: 세션 상태 컬렉션에서 모든 값 및 키를 제거합니다.

trans-unit.source: In implementing the Clear method, you should set the <xref:System.Web.SessionState.ISessionStateItemCollection.Dirty%2A> property to `true` to indicatethatvalues in the <xref:System.Web.SessionState.ISessionStateItemCollection> implementation have been modified.
trans-unit.target: 설정 Clear 메서드를 구현 해야는 <xref:System.Web.SessionState.ISessionStateItemCollection.Dirty%2A>속성을 `true` indicatethatvalues에서 하는 <xref:System.Web.SessionState.ISessionStateItemCollection>구현이 수정 되었습니다.</xref:System.Web.SessionState.ISessionStateItemCollection> </xref:System.Web.SessionState.ISessionStateItemCollection.Dirty%2A>

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets a value indicating whether the collection has been marked as changed.
trans-unit.target: 컬렉션 변경 된 것으로 표시 되었는지 여부를 나타내는 값을 가져오거나 설정 합니다.

trans-unit.source: The Dirty property is used by the <xref:System.Web.SessionState.SessionStateModule> to determine whether the values in an <xref:System.Web.SessionState.ISessionStateItemCollection> implementation have been modified.
trans-unit.target: Dirty 속성은 사용는 <xref:System.Web.SessionState.SessionStateModule>확인 하려면 여부의 값은 <xref:System.Web.SessionState.ISessionStateItemCollection>구현이 수정 되었습니다.</xref:System.Web.SessionState.ISessionStateItemCollection> </xref:System.Web.SessionState.SessionStateModule>

trans-unit.source: In implementing the <xref:System.Web.SessionState.ISessionStateItemCollection> interface, you should initialize the Dirty property as `false` and set the <xref:System.Web.SessionState.SessionStateItemCollection.Dirty%2A> property to `true` in the implementations of the <xref:System.Web.SessionState.ISessionStateItemCollection.Remove%2A>, <xref:System.Web.SessionState.ISessionStateItemCollection.RemoveAt%2A>, or <xref:System.Web.SessionState.ISessionStateItemCollection.Clear%2A> methods.
trans-unit.target: 구현에 <xref:System.Web.SessionState.ISessionStateItemCollection>인터페이스를 더티 속성으로 초기화 해야 `false` 설정 하 고는 <xref:System.Web.SessionState.SessionStateItemCollection.Dirty%2A>속성을 `true` 구현에서는 <xref:System.Web.SessionState.ISessionStateItemCollection.Remove%2A>, <xref:System.Web.SessionState.ISessionStateItemCollection.RemoveAt%2A>, 또는 <xref:System.Web.SessionState.ISessionStateItemCollection.Clear%2A>메서드.</xref:System.Web.SessionState.ISessionStateItemCollection.Clear%2A> </xref:System.Web.SessionState.ISessionStateItemCollection.RemoveAt%2A> </xref:System.Web.SessionState.ISessionStateItemCollection.Remove%2A> </xref:System.Web.SessionState.SessionStateItemCollection.Dirty%2A> </xref:System.Web.SessionState.ISessionStateItemCollection>

trans-unit.source: <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref> if the <xref href="System.Web.SessionState.SessionStateItemCollection"></xref> contents have been changed; otherwise, <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""></xref>.
trans-unit.target: <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref>경우는 <xref href="System.Web.SessionState.SessionStateItemCollection"> </xref> 고, 그렇지 않으면 변경 된 내용을 <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""> </xref>합니다.

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets a value in the collection by numerical index.
trans-unit.target: 숫자 인덱스 별로 컬렉션의 값을 가져오거나 설정 합니다.

trans-unit.source: The numerical index of the value in the collection.
trans-unit.target: 컬렉션에 있는 값의 숫자 인덱스입니다.

trans-unit.source: The value in the collection stored at the specified index.
trans-unit.target: 지정된 된 인덱스에 저장 된 컬렉션의 값입니다.

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets a value in the collection by name.
trans-unit.target: 이름으로 컬렉션의 값을 가져오거나 설정 합니다.

trans-unit.source: The key name of the value in the collection.
trans-unit.target: 컬렉션에 있는 값의 키 이름입니다.

trans-unit.source: The value in the collection with the specified name.
trans-unit.target: 컬렉션에서 지정된 된 이름 가진 값입니다.

trans-unit.source: Gets a collection of the variable names for all values stored in the collection.
trans-unit.target: 변수 이름 컬렉션에 저장 된 모든 값의 컬렉션을 가져옵니다.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Collections.Specialized.NameObjectCollectionBase.KeysCollection> that contains all the collection keys.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Collections.Specialized.NameObjectCollectionBase.KeysCollection>모든 컬렉션 키가 들어 있는.</xref:System.Collections.Specialized.NameObjectCollectionBase.KeysCollection>

trans-unit.source: Deletes an item from the collection.
trans-unit.target: 컬렉션에서 항목을 삭제 합니다.

trans-unit.source: In implementing the Remove method, you should set the <xref:System.Web.SessionState.ISessionStateItemCollection.Dirty%2A> property to `true` to indicatevalues in the <xref:System.Web.SessionState.ISessionStateItemCollection> implementation have been modified.
trans-unit.target: 설정의 Remove 메서드를 구현 해야는 <xref:System.Web.SessionState.ISessionStateItemCollection.Dirty%2A>속성을 `true` indicatevalues에서 하는 <xref:System.Web.SessionState.ISessionStateItemCollection>구현이 수정 되었습니다.</xref:System.Web.SessionState.ISessionStateItemCollection> </xref:System.Web.SessionState.ISessionStateItemCollection.Dirty%2A>

trans-unit.source: If the <xref:System.Web.SessionState.ISessionStateItemCollection> implementation does not contain an element with the specified `name`, the collection should remain unchanged and no exception be thrown.
trans-unit.target: 경우는 <xref:System.Web.SessionState.ISessionStateItemCollection>구현에 지정 된 요소를 포함 하지 `name`이면 컬렉션에 변경 되지 않은 상태로 유지 해야 이며 예외가 throw 됩니다.</xref:System.Web.SessionState.ISessionStateItemCollection>

trans-unit.source: The name of the item to delete from the collection.
trans-unit.target: 컬렉션에서 삭제할 항목의 이름입니다.

trans-unit.source: Deletes an item at a specified index from the collection.
trans-unit.target: 컬렉션에서 지정된 된 인덱스에 항목을 삭제 합니다.

trans-unit.source: In implementing the RemoveAt method, you should set the <xref:System.Web.SessionState.ISessionStateItemCollection.Dirty%2A> property to `true` to indicatevalues in the <xref:System.Web.SessionState.ISessionStateItemCollection> implementation have been modified.
trans-unit.target: 설정 RemoveAt 메서드를 구현 해야는 <xref:System.Web.SessionState.ISessionStateItemCollection.Dirty%2A>속성을 `true` indicatevalues에서 하는 <xref:System.Web.SessionState.ISessionStateItemCollection>구현이 수정 되었습니다.</xref:System.Web.SessionState.ISessionStateItemCollection> </xref:System.Web.SessionState.ISessionStateItemCollection.Dirty%2A>

trans-unit.source: Your implementation of the RemoveAt method should throw an <xref:System.ArgumentOutOfRangeException> exception if `index` is less than zero or is equal to or greater than <xref:System.Collections.ICollection.Count%2A?displayProperty=fullName>.
trans-unit.target: RemoveAt 메서드를 구현할 throw 해야는 <xref:System.ArgumentOutOfRangeException>예외 경우 `index` 가 음수 이거나 <xref:System.Collections.ICollection.Count%2A?displayProperty=fullName>.</xref:System.Collections.ICollection.Count%2A?displayProperty=fullName> 보다 크거나 같으면</xref:System.ArgumentOutOfRangeException>

trans-unit.source: The index of the item to remove from the collection.
trans-unit.target: 컬렉션에서 제거할 항목의 인덱스입니다.
